Then, Accuracy (ACC) is the ratio of total number of predictions that are correct to the total number of predictions made and is given by the Eq. 16.16ACC=TP+TNTP+FP+TN+FN\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
